    <entry>
      <title>微信小程序2</title>
      <link href="/2020/08/12/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F2/"/>
      <url>/2020/08/12/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F2/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>**视频课程：<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1nE41117BQ?p=24" target="_blank" rel="noopener">【WEB前端】零基础玩转微信小程序</a></p></blockquote><h1 id="微信小程序-2"><a href="#微信小程序-2" class="headerlink" title="微信小程序-2"></a>微信小程序-2</h1><h2 id="1-条件渲染"><a href="#1-条件渲染" class="headerlink" title="1 条件渲染"></a>1 条件渲染</h2><blockquote><p>当标签不是平凡切换显示，优先使用wx:if;频繁切换使用hidden</p></blockquote><h3 id="1-1-wx-if"><a href="#1-1-wx-if" class="headerlink" title="1.1 wx:if"></a>1.1 wx:if</h3><p><img src="/2020/08/12/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F2/1.PNG" alt></p><h2 id="1-2-hidden"><a href="#1-2-hidden" class="headerlink" title="1.2 hidden"></a>1.2 hidden</h2><p>1.在标签中直接加入属性：hidden<br>2.<code>hidden=&quot;true&quot;</code><br>3.hidden属性不要和样式display一起使用<br><img src="/2020/08/12/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F2/2.PNG" alt></p><h2 id="2-事件绑定"><a href="#2-事件绑定" class="headerlink" title="2 事件绑定"></a>2 事件绑定</h2><p>1 需要给input标签绑定input事件<br>绑定关键字bindinput<br>2 如何获取输入框的值<br>通过事件源对象来扶取<br><code>e.detail.value</code><br>3 把输入框的值赋值到data当中<br>正确的写法</p><pre class=" language-js"><code class="language-js"><span class="token keyword">this</span> <span class="token function">setData</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>num<span class="token punctuation">:</span>e<span class="token punctuation">.</span>detai1<span class="token punctuation">.</span>value<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> </code></pre><p>4 需要加入一个点击事件</p><ul><li><p>bindtap</p></li><li><p>无法在小程序当中的事件中直按传参</p></li><li><p>通过白定义属性的方式来传递参数</p></li><li><p>事件源中获取自定义属性<br><img src="/2020/08/12/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F2/3.PNG" alt></p><pre class=" language-js"><code class="language-js"><span class="token function">Page</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>  data<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>      num<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token number">0</span>  <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//输入框input事件的执行</span>  <span class="token function">handleinput</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>e<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>      <span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">setData</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>              num<span class="token punctuation">:</span>e<span class="token punctuation">.</span>detail<span class="token punctuation">.</span>value      <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>  <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>  <span class="token function">handletap</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>e<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>      console<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">log</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>e<span class="token punctuation">)</span>      <span class="token keyword">const</span> operation<span class="token operator">=</span>e<span class="token punctuation">.</span>currentTarget<span class="token punctuation">.</span>dataset<span class="token punctuation">.</span>operation<span class="token punctuation">;</span>      <span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">setData</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>          num<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>data<span class="token punctuation">.</span>num<span class="token operator">+</span>operation  <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>  <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span></code></pre></li></ul><h2 id="3-样式wxss"><a href="#3-样式wxss" class="headerlink" title="3 样式wxss"></a>3 样式wxss</h2><h3 id="3-1-导入"><a href="#3-1-导入" class="headerlink" title="3.1 导入"></a>3.1 导入</h3><ul><li>引入的代码是通过 @import来引入</li><li>路径 只能写相对路径<pre class=" language-css"><code class="language-css"><span class="token atrule"><span class="token rule">@import</span><span class="token string">"../../styles/common.wxss"</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></span></code></pre><h2 id="4-选择器与less"><a href="#4-选择器与less" class="headerlink" title="4 选择器与less"></a>4 选择器与less</h2></li><li>略*<h2 id="5-常见组件"><a href="#5-常见组件" class="headerlink" title="5 常见组件"></a>5 常见组件</h2><h3 id="5-1-view"><a href="#5-1-view" class="headerlink" title="5.1 view"></a>5.1 view</h3><table><thead><tr><th>属性</th><th>类型</th><th>默认值</th><th>必填</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>hover-class</td><td>string</td><td>none</td><td>否</td><td>指定按下去的样式类。当 hover-class=”none” 时，没有点击态效果</td></tr><tr><td>hover-stop-propagation</td><td>boolean</td><td>false</td><td>否</td><td>指定是否阻止本节点的祖先节点出现点击态</td></tr><tr><td>hover-start-time</td><td>number</td><td>50</td><td>否</td><td>按住后多久出现点击态，单位毫秒</td></tr><tr><td>hover-stay-time</td><td>number</td><td>400</td><td>否</td><td>手指松开后点击态保留时间，单位毫秒</td></tr></tbody></table></li></ul><h3 id="5-2-text"><a href="#5-2-text" class="headerlink" title="5.2 text"></a>5.2 text</h3><p>1.文本标签<br>2只能嵌喜text<br>3.长技文字可以复制(有该标签有这个功能)<br>4.可以对空格回车进行编码</p><table><thead><tr><th>属性</th><th>类型</th><th>默认值</th><th>必填</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>selectable</td><td>Boolean</td><td>false</td><td>文本是否可选</td></tr><tr><td>decode</td><td>Boolean</td><td>false</td><td>是否解码</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
      
      
