      <title>微信小程序1</title>
      <link href="/2020/08/11/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F1/"/>
      <url>/2020/08/11/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p><strong>视频课程：<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1nE41117BQ?p=17" target="_blank" rel="noopener">【WEB前端】零基础玩转微信小程序</a></strong></p></blockquote><h1 id="微信小程序-1"><a href="#微信小程序-1" class="headerlink" title="微信小程序-1"></a>微信小程序-1</h1><h2 id="原生框架的目录结构"><a href="#原生框架的目录结构" class="headerlink" title="原生框架的目录结构"></a>原生框架的目录结构</h2><ul><li><p><strong>pages</strong></p><ul><li><strong>index</strong>：存放首页的页面文件<ul><li><em>index.js</em> ：逻辑</li><li><em>index.json</em>：配置项</li><li><em>index.wxml</em>：便签嵌套</li><li><em>index.wxss</em>：样式</li></ul></li><li><strong>logs</strong>：日志页面相关文件</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>utils</strong>：可要可不要，帮助文档相关JS</p></li><li><p><strong>app.js</strong>：本小程序的入口文件和全局文件</p></li><li><p><strong>app.json</strong>：全局配置文件，如整个项目的标题名称</p></li><li><p><strong>app.wxss</strong>:全局样式文件</p></li><li><p><strong>project.config.json</strong>：基础配置、环境配置</p></li><li><p><strong>sitemap.json</strong>：配置小程序及其页面是否循序被微信索引</p><h2 id="小程序配置文件"><a href="#小程序配置文件" class="headerlink" title="小程序配置文件"></a>小程序配置文件</h2><h3 id="app-json"><a href="#app-json" class="headerlink" title="app.json"></a>app.json</h3><h4 id="“pages”"><a href="#“pages”" class="headerlink" title="“pages”"></a><strong>“pages”</strong></h4><blockquote><p>本小程序有哪些页面<br>一 一对应pages文件夹中的路径 </p></blockquote><h4 id="“window”"><a href="#“window”" class="headerlink" title="“window”"></a><strong>“window”</strong></h4><blockquote><p>定义小程序所有页面的顶部背景颜色、文字颜色定义等</p></blockquote><p>-<em>backgroundTextstyle</em> ：下拉刷新的所展现的文字颜色<br>-<em>navigationBarBackgroundColor</em> ：导航栏背景颜色<br>-<em>navigationBarTitleText</em> ：导航栏标题名称<br>-<em>navigationBarTextstyle</em> ：导航栏文字颜色（<code>black or white</code>）<br>-<em>enablePullDownRefresh</em> ：全局下拉刷新</p></li></ul><pre><code>      enablePullDownRefresh:true</code></pre><p>  -<em>backgroundColor</em>  ：下拉刷新页面的背景颜色</p><h4 id="“tabbar”"><a href="#“tabbar”" class="headerlink" title="“tabbar”"></a>“tabbar”</h4><p>类似淘宝底部页面的切换<br>在<code>app.josn</code>中添加：输入tabBar回车自动生成如下代码</p><pre class=" language-json"><code class="language-json"><span class="token property">"tabBar"</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token property">"list"</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>      <span class="token property">"pagePath"</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token string">","</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> //要跳转页面的页面路径      <span class="token property">"text"</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token string">"text"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> //标题      <span class="token property">"iconPath"</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token string">"iconPath"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> //未选中图标      <span class="token property">"selectedIconPath"</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token string">"selectedIconPath"</span> //已选中图标    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>  <span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre><p><code>&lt;app.josn&gt;</code><br>如何改变此处<strong>标题颜色</strong>？<code>在list的同级下编写</code></p><pre class=" language-json"><code class="language-json">  <span class="token property">"tabBar"</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token property">"list"</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>      ...    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token property">"color"</span><span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token string">"#0094ff"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token property">"selectedColor"</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token string">"#000000"</span>//只能使用<span class="token number">16</span>进制  <span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre><p><code>&lt;app.josn&gt;</code><br>如何改变<strong>相对位置</strong>？</p><pre class=" language-json"><code class="language-json">  <span class="token property">"tabBar"</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token property">"list"</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>...<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token property">"color"</span><span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token string">"#0094ff"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token property">"selectedColor"</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token string">"#000000"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token property">"position"</span><span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token string">"top"</span> //未设置的话默认在bottom，tabbar在顶部时默认不显示图标  <span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre><p><code>&lt;app.josn&gt;</code></p><h3 id="page-json"><a href="#page-json" class="headerlink" title="page.json"></a>page.json</h3><blockquote><p>独立定义每一个页面的一些属性，如颜色等</p></blockquote><p>page.json用法与app.json中的Windo类似，其他使用参考小程序文档</p><h3 id="sitemap-json"><a href="#sitemap-json" class="headerlink" title="sitemap.json"></a>sitemap.json</h3><blockquote><p>了解即可</p></blockquote><h2 id="模板语法"><a href="#模板语法" class="headerlink" title="模板语法"></a>模板语法</h2><h3 id="数据绑定"><a href="#数据绑定" class="headerlink" title="数据绑定"></a>数据绑定</h3><table><thead><tr><th align="left">标签</th><th align="center">作用</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">text</td><td align="center">行内标签，默认不换行</td></tr><tr><td align="left">view</td><td align="center">块级标签，默认换行</td></tr></tbody></table><p>页面中显示的数据放在目标页面/XXX.js的data中</p><pre class=" language-js"><code class="language-js"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// pages/test/test.js</span><span class="token function">Page</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    data<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>    msg<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">"hello!world"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    num<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token number">10000</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    isBoy<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token boolean">false</span>，    person<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        age<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token number">74</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        height<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token number">145</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        weight<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token number">45</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>         name<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">"小王"</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    ischecked<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token boolean">false</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></code></pre><p><code>test.wxml</code><br><img src="/2020/08/11/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F1/1.PNG" alt></p><h2 id="运算"><a href="#运算" class="headerlink" title="运算"></a>运算</h2><p>1.数字加减<br>2.字符串拼接<br>3.三元表达式<br><img src="/2020/08/11/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F1/2.PNG" alt></p><h2 id="数组和对象循环"><a href="#数组和对象循环" class="headerlink" title="数组和对象循环"></a>数组和对象循环</h2><h3 id="列表循环"><a href="#列表循环" class="headerlink" title="列表循环"></a>列表循环</h3><p>wx:for=“”<br>wx:for-item=”循环项的名称”<br>wx:for-index=”循环项的索引”</p><pre class=" language-js"><code class="language-js"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// pages/test/test.js</span><span class="token function">Page</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    data<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        list<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span>            <span class="token punctuation">{</span>                id<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>                name<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">"小李"</span>            <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>            <span class="token punctuation">{</span>                id<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>                name<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">"amy"</span>            <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>            <span class="token punctuation">{</span>                id<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>                name<span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">"tony"</span>            <span class="token punctuation">}</span>        <span class="token punctuation">]</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></code></pre><pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>view</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>view</span> <span class="token attr-name"><span class="token namespace">wx:</span>for</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>{{list}}<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span>     <span class="token attr-name"><span class="token namespace">wx:</span>for-item</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>item<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span>     <span class="token attr-name"><span class="token namespace">wx:</span>for-index</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>index<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    索引：{{index}}    --    值：{{item.name}}    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>view</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>view</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre><p><code>wx:key</code>=”唯一的值”提高列表渲染的性能<br>1 <code>wx:key</code>绑定个普通的字符串的时候 那么这个字符串名称肯定是循环数组中的对象的 唯一属性<br>2 <code>wx:key =&quot;*this&quot;</code> 就表示I你的数组是一个普通的数组 *this 表示是循环项<br>普通数组[1,2,3,44,5]</p><pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>view</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>view</span> <span class="token attr-name"><span class="token namespace">wx:</span>for</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>{{list}}<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span>     <span class="token attr-name"><span class="token namespace">wx:</span>for-item</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>item<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span>     <span class="token attr-name"><span class="token namespace">wx:</span>for-index</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>index<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span>    <span class="token attr-name"><span class="token namespace">wx:</span>key</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>id<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    索引：{{index}}    --    值：{{item.name}}    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>view</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>view</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre><p>3当出现数组的嵌套循环的时候尤其要注意 以下绑定的名称不要重名<br><code>wx:for- item=”item&quot; wx : for- index=”index&quot;</code><br>4默认情况下我们不写<br><code>Wx: for- item=&quot; item&quot; WX : for - index=”index&quot;</code><br>小程序也会把循环项的名称和索引的名称item 和index<br>只有一层循环的话(<code>wx :for item=&quot; item&quot; wx: for- index=&quot;index&quot;</code>) 可以省略</p><h3 id="对象循环"><a href="#对象循环" class="headerlink" title="对象循环"></a>对象循环</h3><p><code>Wx :for=&quot;&quot; wx:for-item=&quot;对 象的值&quot; wX : for- index=&quot;对象的属性”</code><br>==循环对象的时候最好把item和index的名称都修改一下==<br>wx: for-item= “value”<br>WX : for- index= “key’</p><pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>view</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>view</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>对象循环<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>view</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>view</span> <span class="token attr-name"><span class="token namespace">wx:</span>for</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>{{person}}<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span>     <span class="token attr-name"><span class="token namespace">wx:</span>for-item</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>value<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span>     <span class="token attr-name"><span class="token namespace">wx:</span>for-index</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>key<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span>    <span class="token attr-name"><span class="token namespace">wx:</span>key</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>age<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>        属性：{{key}}        --        值：{{value}}    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>view</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>view</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
